	</ul>
</div>

        
	
<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Habitats</h4>
	<div class="text"> Extreme rich fens from montane to alpine sites. Soils may peaty. The USFWS Wetland Inventory (1996 national list) recognizes <i>Kobresia myosuroides</i> as a FACW plant. </div>
</div>

        
