    <div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
        <h4 class="header">Regional Status</h4>
        

        <ul class="text">
        
            <li><b>Sierra Nevada</b> (M261Eo). Cooper and Wolf (2006) sampled two extremely nutrient-rich fens in the Convict Creek drainage and described the <i>Kobresia myosuroides-Thalictrum alpinum</i> type and the <i>Trichophorum pumilum-Carex scirpoidea</i> type. We place the first in this alliance and the other in a list of unranked associations.</li>
        
        </ul>
    </div>


    
	
